Title: Squash Those Foul Odors
Description:
Grandpa always said, "A squash a week, and your tail won't reek."

<Yoon subtly sniffs the air.>

Yup. I think it's been about a week. Could you help me plant a Jade Squash?
ObjectivesText: Plant a Jade Squash in Sunsong Ranch. You can purchase seeds from Merchant Greenfield in the Halfhill Market.
